data.description: READY FOR MOVE-IN. COMFORTABLE. SPACIOUS – Forest Grove of Palm Harbor!!  If you don't know now you know.  One of the most desirable communities in Palm Harbor, Florida.  You'll find mature landscaping and palm trees, beautifully maintained homes and a community that comes together to celebrate life and holidays.  Located in one of the best rated school districts in Pinellas County, a short bike or walk to downtown Palm Harbor, the Pinellas Trail, local schools and then you will want to take a drive to Honeymoon Island but it's only a few minutes away. Check out this 2 bedroom and 2 bath, split floor plan home with an oversized living and entertaining area. As you walk into the home you are greeted with an abundance of natural light, clean and crisp feeling throughout, and a spacious cozy living area. The primary bedroom with the ensuite has a large walk-in closet with its own private door to the oversized side yard and a large. The 2nd bedroom is across the home which makes the bedrooms feel more private. The BRAND NEW kitchen with white cabinets, quartz countertops, tile backsplash is a must see in person! This nice corner lot home has two great large side yards to make your own for great entertainment and gatherings. Major Components (4-Point items): Roof is 2019, Water Heater is 2021, Electrical Panel is insurable, and the HVAC is 2011, which has been maintained and serviced regularly. This is a NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE and there is NO HOA! Why are so many people making Palm Harbor and north Pinellas County their home? Schedule your private tour of this home today, grab lunch in downtown Palm Harbor and find out why.
